        "description": "Commercial CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R1) with documented version control, release notes, and regression test suite. User-defined hemolysis subroutine under configuration management with change-log and peer review records."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 is a commercially validated solver with a published regression test suite. The in-house hemolysis power-law UDF is version-controlled in a Git repository with peer-reviewed commit history and documented unit tests covering the Giersiepen and modified Heuser–Opitz damage models. SQA requirements for MRL 2 (Gradation 2) are fully met."
    },
    {
