      "rationale": "Formal equivalency mapping between validation-experiment input parameters and COU simulation inputs (beyond the qualitative mapping documented in VR-GCBP-2024-01 Section 4) is not required at MRL 2 for this Class II device. The validation and COU share the same geometry, fluid, and operating envelope, making parameter equivalency straightforward. A formal equivalency matrix is reserved for higher MRL assessments."
